headline: AvalonBay Communities, Inc. Announces Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., July 10, 2025--AVALONBAY COMMUNITIES, INC. (NYSE: AVB) (the "Company") will release its second quarter 2025 earnings on July 30, 2025 after the market close. The Company will hold a conference call on July 31, 2025 at 1:00 PM Eastern Time (ET) to discuss its second quarter 2025 results.
